        "details": {
            "description": "<p>Hi welcome to our home this is a unique space that is designed with a contemporary look in mind room</p><p><br></p><p>Primary set up for a single guest who is looking for short stays this is a stunning guest room at the end of our driveway on the ground floor so it stays pretty cool in all weathers . The room has fast wifi and a smart TV with Netflix / amazon / Sony liv and even hot-star that i can log you in on request</p><h2>The space</h2><ol><li>Key elements of this room are</li><li>its on on the ground floor which makes it great for older couples</li><li>It is totally independent from the main house which gives guests 100% privacy and independent access</li><li>The lighting is very modern and contemporary</li><li>There is one large window for air but there is almost no natural light hitting the room as its on the lower floor of a very large house - some people prefer this as it keeps the heat away but it is as it is</li><li>There is a Samsung Smart TV with Netflix / Sony Liv / Amazon prime / Amazon music / Hotstar / Zee 5</li></ol><h2>Guest access</h2><p>Guest have there own private access via the driveway which can be used to smoke as well - guest can smoke in our lawn as well</p><h2>Other things to note</h2><p>Guest will have to inform us to turn on the AC either before they arrive or as soon as they check in. The ac can only be accessed once we trigger the access via a smart devices.</p><p><br></p><p>This space is designated for single traveler only - we dont host couples here - we also don't allow guests</p><p><br></p><p>We don't server breakfast but I can get you in touch with a tiffin service that delivers at 9 am</p><p><br></p><p>All laundry items will be washed using gentle wash and give the next day</p><p><br></p><p>There is a limit of 10 items , per guest per week cloth count above this is chargeable at 15 rs per item</p><p><br></p><p>We provide air purifiers and heaters on request and these are chargeable on pay as you go basis an air purifier is charged at 150 rs per night these items must be requested before you arrive .</p><p><br></p><p>We don't host locals with a Delhi ID as the law of the city does not allow guests to book locally</p><p><br></p><p>GYM ACCESS</p><p>Starting 15 December guests will not have access to our personal gym anymore as we will be upgrading the place - Guest can still use a public gym at pacific sports complex which is 1 km away from the house they take 500 per use</p>",
